<HEADLINE>
READY FOR PRIME TIME, HERE COMES THE CHIEF JUSTICE 
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(Editors: also see EDIT-OBSERVER-IMPEACH-REHNQUIST, which moved
Friday night) 
(ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
