<HEADLINE>
THE STALEMATE LIVES ON AFTER THE BOMBING
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By SERGE SCHMEMANN   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
