</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-GERM-WARFARE-REVIEW-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE THREAT OF GERM WEAPONS IS RISING. FEAR, TOO.
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By WILLIAM J. BROAD and JUDITH MILLER   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
