<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    The last word on a scary economy
 &HT;    By Marilyn Geewax
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Only once every 1,000 years does a scribe get a chance
