   SCHUETT-COLUMN _ GIBSONBURG, Ohio _ This column is not for the
squeamish. It's ugly and it's personal. It's about runny noses.
Everybody in the eighth grade seems to have one. (Schuett, Cox News
Service) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   YOUNG-COLUMN _ WACO, Texas _ Having made the unforgivable
mistake of trying to take New Road from Valley Mills Drive to
Franklin Avenue on an early pre-Christmas evening, I had time to
ponder the future. I had time because the traffic was backed up.
(Young, Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED
