. 
MAYA-MOVIE (Los Angeles) _ She enters a room quietly, speaks with
the utmost cordiality, takes care not to raise her naturally
resonant voice above a certain polite volume. All that considered,
Maya Angelou commands your complete, undivided attention. By Bob
