. 
FIT-TV (Los Angeles) _ By the time New Year's Eve has come and
gone, there you'll be, just like last year: overweight, overtired
and overextended. And vowing that you'll shape up. But this year,
help could be as close as your television remote control. Fit tv, a
reinvented health-and-fitness cable channel, will hit the airwaves
about the time the big, lighted ball drops in Times Square. (With
sidebar, FITTV-SHOWS) By Carol Bidwell. 
. 

<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-12-28-98 1626EST &QL; 
