career with a postseason appearance in the Peach Bowl, losing to
Virginia in Ray Goff's final game in 1995. Three seasons later, the
Bulldogs are back in the Peach and back to face Virginia. The
seniors hope to have a different outcome against Virginia on this
occasion. (Schlabach, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
