receiver. We know that. But folks in Tallahassee say he is much
more. Like Deion Sanders at cornerback, like Warrick Dunn at
tailback, like Marvin Jones at linebacker, Warrick will leave
Florida State as the definitive player at his position. At Florida
State, that a pretty big deal. (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
