<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ARCH-MOBILEMEDIA (Undated) -- Arch Communications Group's
planned acquisition of troubled pager giant MobileMedia Corp. could
run afoul of a group of the latter's bondholders, who say they may
have enough votes to scuttle the deal. By Steven Wilmsen. 400
words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
