   FBN-PATRIOTS (Foxborough, Mass.) -- Coach Pete Carroll takes a
philosophical view of Sunday's loss to the Jets. By Nick Cafardo.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-BRUINS-CAPS (Odenton, Md.) _ By Nancy Marrapese.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
