<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Dec. 29 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Eddie Ibardolasa at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BKC-HARRICK (Los Angeles) _ Feature story on Rhode Island
basketball coach Jim Harrick, the former UCLA and Pepperdine coach
who returns for his first game in the Southern California since his
ouster at UCLA. Rhode Island plays Pepperdine on Tuesday. 
By Brian Dohn. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
FBC-ROSEBOWL-1994 (Los Angeles) _ A look back at the 1994 Rose
