   MIGRAINE-DRUGS (Undated) _ The growing number of migraine
medications entering the market represents a gamble by the world's
drug makers. They are betting that prescriptions for the drugs will
continue to grow at a rate that will allow every competitor to make
robust profits. By David J. Morrow.
