<P>
   FBN-PLAYOFFS (Undated) _ An On Pro Football column on the NFL
playoffs, which begin next weekend with four first-round games, one
of them (Jacksonville vs. New England) involving two teams whose
starting quarterbacks have been sidelined with injuries and may or
may not be ready to play. By Thomas George.
