<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BKC-HARRICK-CORRECTION-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HARRICK RETURNS TO WHERE IT ALL BEGAN
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Fixes Harrick in headline) 
By BRIAN DOHN  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
